g.title: j3586635625
g.text: Where'd you learn to fight?

g.title: j1278624375
g.text: Trial and error.

g.title: j1248580533
g.text: A mentor of mine, named Teshin.

g.title: j3426972941
g.text: [Ignore.]

g.title: j552538681
g.text: Sounds like a great way to get killed.

g.title: j104558720
g.text: An elite Dax soldier- which I *just* remembered means nothing to you.

g.title: Chat ends.
g.text: Chat ends.

g.title: j1162161122
g.text: Oh, and I did. A lot. Over, and over, and over... And over...

g.title: j276150237
g.text: I'll summarize. It means he has the patience to put up with me.

g.title: j4243071319
g.text: And over...

g.title: j1992025473
g.text: Heh. Sounds like a hell of a tutor. And someone I'd like to meet.

g.title: j3950109267
g.text: In Duviri, in that loop you told me about.

g.title: j3041878944
g.text: I'd still be lost in Duviri if it weren't for him.

g.title: j996934694
g.text: He gave me the push I needed.

g.title: j855434315
g.text: It's more of a spiral, really. Point being, I got a lot of practice.

g.title: j1615179752
g.text: I really don't want to talk about this. [End.]

g.title: j933837537
g.text: Sounds like he gave you the push you needed.

g.title: j3479582678
g.text: We all need that person, sometimes.

g.title: j622637296
g.text: Nothing teaches you how to fight like knowing exactly what you're trying to avoid.

g.title: j1656601153
g.text: Yeah. And he coached me on how to fight. On how to beat Dominus Thrax.

g.title: j3320312875
g.text: Sol. I can understand that feeling, though I've never died.

g.title: j1289264635
g.text: Thrax was... a character from a story, right?

g.title: j570361536
g.text: I... well... you have, though. Don't you remember?

g.title: j1138943285
g.text: It's not exactly something most people have to deal with.

g.title: j1389507212
g.text: That I accidentally turned into a tyrannical despot who had me executed in creative ways for centuries? Yep.

g.title: j1624854403
g.text: I don't, really...It's hazy. And I'm glad for it.

g.title: j3760651536
g.text: I died so many times, I stopped caring.

g.title: j2938904752
g.text: But... why?

g.title: j4155636144
g.text: Yeah. Because if you did, you might wind up like *me.* [End.]

g.title: j3720575444
g.text: Honestly? You're lucky it's hazy. I died so many times, I stopped caring.

g.title: j393369266
g.text: +10 Chemistry

g.title: j1502713374
g.text: How'd you feel if I asked you that question?

g.title: j1231813393
g.text: You volunteering to be my therapist?

g.title: j3437703748
g.text: Being trapped alone in the Void does weird things to you.

g.title: j157269187
g.text: I can't do this right now. [End.]

g.title: j2171884134
g.text: That's not what I - whatever.

g.title: j2456855838
g.text: How could you stop caring?

g.title: j27631470
g.text: +10 Chemistry

g.title: j2245461255
g.text: Hard pass.

g.title: j2429459347
g.text: That's fair. How about we come back to it, should we get to that point?

g.title: j1110960774
g.text: Deal.

g.title: j16657763
g.text: Pass.

g.title: j1992354670
g.text: Boolean ArthurDuviri is now true.

g.title: j1153756766
g.text: Well, good talk, then.
